1. Good luck.  I won 6 games by good luck. (but dont' expect it, you should expect yourself)

Deep analizing. Try to cuaculat every variant you can, and to find which variant is good for you. It's a dull work and an interesting work at the same time.  It's  not like the games face by face, you have planty of time to analyse. So take it easy. And good luck to you all.
